        },
        {
            "title": "歐洲天然氣價格單周有望飆升20% 「完美風暴」擾動市場情緒",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> （本文為機器翻譯，準確性基於第三方軟件服務，反饋請點擊）</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲天然氣價格將迎來逾兩年最大單周漲幅，異常寒冷天氣引發交易員爭相回補空頭頭寸，市場情緒正發生轉變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周基準期貨漲幅將超過20%，打破了持續數月的窄幅震盪格局。此次上漲標志著市場格局的重大轉變，強勁的供暖需求與重燃的地緣政治風險形成疊加效應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Global Risk Management首席分析師Arne Lohmann Rasmussen表示，「市場情緒已徹底逆轉，堪稱完美風暴。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f32945ac-71a5-3ff5-85e0-3b0afbbbe27f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去年末，得益於強勁的燃料進口和溫和的冬季開端，市場對該地區供應緩衝的信心推動歐洲天然氣淨空頭頭寸達到2020年初以來最悲觀水平。隨著對該地區供應前景的擔憂加劇，押注市場走弱的投機者開始買入期貨平倉，從而助推了近期漲勢。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qodlB4.uVzVcENluEQQELw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8a5a1b2521602111302abf11a29dfbb7\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿姆斯特丹時間10:02，歐洲天然氣基準荷蘭近月期貨上漲4.7%，報每兆瓦時34.73歐元。周漲幅有望創下2023年10月以來最大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題European Gas Jumps 20% on Week as ‘Perfect Storm’ Hits Sentiment</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Elena Mazneva、Joe Wertz.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E6%B0%A3%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%96%AE%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%8720-%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4-%E6%93%BE%E5%8B%95%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92-091800252.html",
